Field DateSampleCollected After //This business rule calculates Days Acute based on the values entered // in the Date Onset field of the Case Report Form and the Date Sample Collected // in the current form. ASSIGN DaysAcute = DAYS(CaseInformationForm.DateOnset, DateSampleCollected ) IF DateSampleCollected <DateOnset THEN DIALOG "Date of sample collected must be equal or greater than date of onset. Please verify your date." TITLETEXT="Alert" CLEAR DateSampleCollected GOTO DateSampleCollected END-IF
End-After End-Field
Field SampleInterpret After
IF SampleInterpret = "3" AND DaysAcute < 3 THEN DIALOG "The sample was collected less than 3 days after symptom onset, therefore it is necessary to select 'Negative, needs followup sample'" CLEAR SampleInterpret END-IF
//add code here ASSIGN SAMPLE = SampleInterpret
End-After End-Field
